{
  "texts": [
    "AI-enabled IRS-ISACThe IRS is a meta-surface, consisting of a large number of passive reflection elements.",
    "By changing the amplitude and phase shift of each reflection element intelligently, the IRS can reconfigure the wireless propagation environment, making it an enabler for wireless communications [260].",
    "Owing to the passive nature, the IRS is superior to the traditional active relay in power consumption and deployment flexibility.",
    "Integrating the IRS into ISAC is beneficial to both communication and sensing performance by enhancing the links.",
    "Nevertheless, the introduction of IRS makes the system design more complicated and challenging."
  ]
}